2nd level (3 slots): lesser restoration, spiritual weapon
3rd level (2 slots): dispel magic, spirit guardians

Priests bring the teachings of their gods to the common folk. They are the spiritual leaders of temples and shrines
often hold positions of influence in their communities. Evil priests might work openly under a tyrant, or they might be the
leaders of religious sects hidden in the shadows of good society, overseeing depraved rites.
A priest typically has one or more acolytes to help with religious ceremonies and other sacred duties.

bounty hunters, serve as guides, or provide military reconnaissance.
